snippet.title: Scoop Kick! SAGE 2021 Teaser Trailer (FULL GAME OUT NOW)
snippet.description:
GET THE FULL GAME FROM STEAM:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1866990/Scoop_Kick/

A game inspired by some of my favourite arcade games, such as Burger Time and Dig Dug.
In this game you control Ms. Cream on a quest to retrieve all the stolen ice cream from the evil Juice Bunch.

Follow me on Twitter for news and updates:
https://twitter.com/Ryemanni
